Worst Elmo video I've seen in a long time. My handicapped child ADORES Elmo, but she will NOT watch this one. I thought it was just because it was new, so I sat down to watch it with her; it is unwatchable. Over 1/2 of the movie features Elmo TALKING/jumping in front of the colored squared background you see on the cover, then they cut to scenes of kids playing in playgrounds jumping around. Not your typical Elmo by far. Most of these are compilations of previously scene show spliced together to make a longer movie-we get that-but this is hideous.
I love that this video gets my toddler up and moving!
for my grand child !! He loves it ...

I purchased the Sesame Street: Play All Day Elmo video for my three year old great niece after I saw the NBC Today show's feature of Elmo and his Sesame Street friends lead some of the staff's children through a few of the activities available on the video. It looked like so much fun! My nephew and his wife report that she loves the games, activities and songs and often asks for the Play All Day Elmo video. Gotta love anything that entertains a three year old for hours.
my son loves elmo, he really liked this one but it had too much real life in it. where it showed kids playing wish it more of just elmo

The DVD cover and rscription say " 2 hours of fun", but the actual movie is only about 40-45minutes. I guess They're including the previews and other "bonus" features in the 2 hours. She loves the movie but I was looking for and Elmo movie that was longer than 1 hour not including all that other "fluff " that we fast forward through.
